          "process_md": "> ***Registration Process:***\n\n**Step-01:** The applicant visits the [official website](https://fisheries.bihar.gov.in/Default.aspx) and clicks the &quot;Applications are being invited for all the schemes of the financial year (2024-25), [click here](https://fisheries.bihar.gov.in/Accordion.aspx) to apply&quot;. \n**Step-02:** Select the &quot;[Registration for Fisheries Schemes](https://misfisheries.bihar.gov.in/RegisterFisheries.aspx)&quot;\n**Step-03:** Select the category: Individual and complete all basic details of the applicant for registration, including category, caste, applicant name, date of birth, address, bank details, etc.\n**Step-04:** Enter a valid 10-digit mobile number and click to send OTP.\n**Step-05:** An OTP will be sent to the provided mobile number.\n**Step-06:** Enter the OTP; after verification of the OTP, you will receive a Registration Number and Password.\n**Step-07:** Click on the &quot;Login&quot; and enter the Registration Number and Password.\n<br>\n\n> ***Application Form Filling Process:***\n\n**Step-01:** The applicant visits the [official website](https://fisheries.bihar.gov.in/Default.aspx) and clicks the &quot;Applications are being invited for all the schemes of the financial year (2024-25), [click here](https://fisheries.bihar.gov.in/Accordion.aspx) to apply&quot;.\n**Step-02:** Click &quot;If your already register, [login here](https://misfisheries.bihar.gov.in/login.aspx)&quot;. \n**Step-03**: Select &quot;Scheme name&quot; under the &quot;Matsya Yojana&quot; option on the top menu.\n**Step-04:** Applicant need to provide the following details :\n\n\n  - Details of individual (applicant/group leader)\n  - Permanent address\n  - Bank account details\n  - Land/pond details\n\n\n**Step-05**: Upload the required documents.\n**Step-06:** Click on the submit button as well print the application form and submit it to the District Fisheries Office along with attachments. \n<br>\n\nNote: Download the [Affidavit form](https://misfisheries.bihar.gov.in/Docs/Specialpackagesapat.pdf) and [Consent form](https://misfisheries.bihar.gov.in/Docs/specialpackagesahmati.pdf) also attached with the application. \n"
        }
