      "eligibilityCriteria": {
        "eligibilityDescription_md": "\n1. The applicant must own or lease land in the identified plateau-dominated districts. \n1. A person/family should construct a pond of a maximum of one acre and a minimum 0.4-acre water area i.e. 0.5-acre area.\n1. The applicant should install a concrete board on the pond. \n1. The board should be made of an iron sheet of size 4 feet x 3 feet, standing four feet at an iron angle, on which the description will be written with paint.\n\n",
